title: [RG.REBOOT] Dubstep Sampler Vol.2 (2013) {MP3-320CBR}
description:
Music Notes 
 	~~~~~~~~~~~
	Compiled from WEB sources. Personally arranged by REBOOT.OP.

	This release features a few trap songs, along with Glitch Hop and a re-appearence of
	a song from the previous volume. Find it and you will be rewarded haha. (jk)

	If you want a Vol.3, please comment with the request. I put together songs that
	most people have not heard or are new.
